trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the culture of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的文化特性。

trans-unit.target: 表示組件之文化特性的字串。

trans-unit.target: 空白的字串表示不因文化特性而異。

trans-unit.source: The full name of the assembly, also known as the display name.
trans-unit.target: 組件的完整名稱，也稱為顯示名稱。

trans-unit.source: Parses string to obtain an assembly identity.
trans-unit.target: 剖析字串以取得組件識別。

trans-unit.source: Returns null if identity could not be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 如果無法取得識別，則傳回 null。

trans-unit.source: The resulting assembly identity.
trans-unit.target: 產生的組件識別。

trans-unit.source: The name of the file from which the identity is to be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 從中取得識別的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: Obtains identity of the specified assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得所指定組件的識別。

trans-unit.source: File can be a PE with an embedded xml manifest, a stand-alone xml manifest file, or a .NET assembly.
trans-unit.target: 可以是具有內嵌 XML 資訊清單、獨立 XML 資訊清單檔案或 .NET 組件的 PE 檔案。

trans-unit.source: Returns null if identity could not be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 如果無法取得識別，則傳回 null。

trans-unit.source: The assembly identity of the specified file.
trans-unit.target: 所指定檔案的組件識別。

trans-unit.source: The name of the file from which the identity is to be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 從中取得識別的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: Obtains identity of the specified .NET assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得所指定 .NET 組件的識別。

trans-unit.source: File must be a .NET assembly.
trans-unit.target: 檔案必須是 .NET 組件。

trans-unit.source: Returns null if identity could not be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 如果無法取得識別，則傳回 null。

trans-unit.source: The assembly identity of the specified file.
trans-unit.target: 所指定檔案的組件識別。

trans-unit.source: The name of the file from which the identity is to be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 從中取得識別的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: Obtains identity of the specified manifest file.
trans-unit.target: 取得所指定資訊清單檔的識別。

trans-unit.source: File must be a standalone XML manifest file.
trans-unit.target: 檔案必須是獨立 XML 資訊清單檔。

trans-unit.source: Returns null if identity could not be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 如果無法取得識別，則傳回 null。

trans-unit.source: The assembly identity of the specified file.

trans-unit.source: The name of the file from which the identity is to be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 從中取得識別的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: Obtains identity of the specified native assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得所指定原生組譯碼的識別。

trans-unit.source: File must be either a PE with an embedded XML manifest, or a stand-alone XML manifest file.
trans-unit.target: 檔案必須是具有內嵌 XML 資訊清單或獨立 XML 資訊清單檔案的 PE 檔案。

trans-unit.source: Returns NULL if identity could not be obtained.
trans-unit.target: 如果無法取得識別，則傳回 NULL。

trans-unit.source: The assembly identity of the specified file.
trans-unit.target: 所指定檔案的組件識別。

trans-unit.source: Specifies which attributes to be included in the full name.
trans-unit.target: 指定要包含在完整名稱中的屬性。

trans-unit.source: Returns the full name of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 傳回組件的完整名稱。

trans-unit.source: A string representation of the full name.
trans-unit.target: 完整名稱的字串表示。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="True" /> if this assembly is part of the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: 如果這個組件是 .NET Framework 的一部分，則傳回 <see langword="True" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="Boolean" /> value indicating whether this assembly is part of the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Boolean" /> 值，表示這個組件是否為 .NET Framework 的一部分。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if this assembly is part of the .NET Framework; otherwise <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這個組件是 .NET Framework 的一部分，則為 <see langword="True" />，否則為 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the assembly identity represents a neutral platform assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出組件識別是否表示非平台相關組件。

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="Boolean" /> value indicating whether the assembly identity represents a neutral platform assembly.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Boolean" /> 值，這個值表示組件識別是否表示中性平台組件。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the assembly identity is a neutral platform assembly; otherwise <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果組件識別為中性平台組件，則為 <see langword="True" />，否則為 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the assembly identity is a strong name.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，這個值表示組件識別是否為強式名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="Boolean" /> value indicating whether the assembly identity is a strong name.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Boolean" /> 值，這個值表示組件識別是否為強式名稱。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the assembly identity is a strong name; otherwise <see langword="False" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果組件識別為強式名稱，則為 <see langword="True" />，否則為 <see langword="False" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the simple name of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的簡單名稱。

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the simple name of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 字串，表示組件的簡單名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the processor architecture of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的處理器架構。

trans-unit.source: A string representing the processor architecture of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 代表組件處理器架構的字串。

trans-unit.source: Valid values are `msil`, `x86`, `ia64`, `amd64`.
trans-unit.target: 有效值為`msil`， `x86`， `ia64`， `amd64`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the public key token of the assembly, which is the last 8 bytes of the SHA-1 hash of the public key under which the assembly is signed.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的公開金鑰語彙基元，是用以簽署組件之公開金鑰的 SHA-1 雜湊最後 8 個位元組。

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the public key token of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 字串，表示該組件的公開金鑰語彙基元。

trans-unit.source: Returns the full ClickOnce assembly identity.
trans-unit.target: 傳回完整的 ClickOnce 組件識別。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type attribute of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的類型屬性。

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the type attribute of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 字串，表示組件的類型屬性。

trans-unit.source: Valid values are `win32` or a blank string.
trans-unit.target: 有效值為 `win32` 或空白字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the version of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定組件的版本。

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the assembly version.
trans-unit.target: 字串，表示組件版本。
